Each a element must contain text or an img with an alt attribute.

A link name allows screen readers to voice what the links does. If there is no link text or the `alt` text is blank, screen readers have nothing to read, so read out the URL instead. To add a name do one of the following:

  • Add text between the a element start and end tags
  • Add an aria-label attribute
  • Add an aria-labelledby attribute
  • Add an img alt attribute if the link contains an img element

3379

Each a element must contain text or an img with an alt attribute.

A link name allows screen readers to voice what the links does. If there is no link text or the `alt` text is blank, screen readers have nothing to read, so read out the URL instead. To add a name do one of the following:

  • Add text between the a element start and end tags
  • Add an aria-label attribute
  • Add an aria-labelledby attribute
  • Add an img alt attribute if the link contains an img element
Line 3379 WCAG 2.1 A F89 Section 508 (2017) A F89

Add an aria-label or aria-labelledby attribute describing the image. Purely decorative images should use role=presentation.

Line 3438 WCAG 2.1 A F65 Section 508 (2017) A F65

<div class="image-row-background-image ec-e-bd-bbe-fdaf-imageRowItem ImageRow-module_backgroundImage__1kV1k" role="img" aria-label=""></div>

3439 </a>

3440 </div>

3441 <div class="image-row-background-image-top-container ImageRow-module_topLevelContainer__1c5nZ fbcec-b-acc-f-dbea-border&#10; undefined&#10; ImageRow-module_fade__1QSlq ImageRow-module_rowDisplay__2RhIL ImageRow-module_center__3p0oi&#10; &#10; &#10; ImageRow-module_biColumn__1XUWJ undefined&#10; " style="transform: translateX(0%) translateX(0px);">

3442

Each a element must contain text or an img with an alt attribute.

A link name allows screen readers to voice what the links does. If there is no link text or the `alt` text is blank, screen readers have nothing to read, so read out the URL instead. To add a name do one of the following:

  • Add text between the a element start and end tags
  • Add an aria-label attribute
  • Add an aria-labelledby attribute
  • Add an img alt attribute if the link contains an img element
Line 3442 WCAG 2.1 A F89 Section 508 (2017) A F89
